snippet.title: Voidrun Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the demo or purchase full version on :
itch.io : https://benjamin-soul.itch.io/voidrun
steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1048560/Voidrun/

The Void will consume each parts of our universe.
Until then, as his underling you are asked to wipe out all life forms on four planets.
For this task The Void will grant you four gifts. Don't become attached to them because what the Void give, the Void will take back.
